Field Detail

MERGE_GROUPS

public static final java.lang.String MERGE_GROUPS
A leader suggests another leader to merge their groups.

This normally happens as a result of a MessageSubjects.GROUP_CREATED_NOTIFICATION message or if the leader wants to re-order its group.

The recipient will reply with GroupLeaderCommandAck.KO if it rejects the merge, if it is not the group leader or if it has already a parent group.

The recipient will reply with GroupLeaderCommandAck.OK if it has accepted the caller as it new group parent.

Note that since the two leaders are managing two different group they will have a different group id. The merge its possible only if the two groups tuple description matches.

Constant Field Values

JOIN_MY_GROUP

public static final java.lang.String JOIN_MY_GROUP
The group leader ask a remote node to join its group. If the remote node leads a group matching the current one the remote group should leave its group and join this one.

A leader ask a follower of a group in the same hierarchy to move to a different child group.

ADOPT_GROUP

public static final java.lang.String ADOPT_GROUP
A group leader is asking another group leader to become its parent group. This often happens when a leader is collapsed and the new leader wants to rejoin the previous hierarchy.
